    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Car Service Simulator 结合了真实的汽车维修、改装、商业管理和开放世界探索！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经营自己的汽车维修店，修理和改装车辆，发展业务，并探索动态世界，成为汽车行业的传奇！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062150/extras/4fd4a94391fe2734273b4f7a35b4caef.poster.avif?t=1756490723\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062150/extras/4fd4a94391fe2734273b4f7a35b4caef.webm?t=1756490723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062150/extras/4fd4a94391fe2734273b4f7a35b4caef.mp4?t=1756490723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔧 主要特点</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为汽车维修与保养专家:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用专业工具诊断和修理发动机、刹车、悬挂和变速器。更换老旧零件，重建发动机，完成复杂维修。提升技能，挑战更大任务，成为最受欢迎的汽车专家！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062150/extras/23fec1bd2b77366e6f89c5f12bb70315.poster.avif?t=1756490723\" width=792 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062150/extras/23fec1bd2b77366e6f89c5f12bb70315.webm?t=1756490723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062150/extras/23fec1bd2b77366e6f89c5f12bb70315.mp4?t=1756490723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>改装和升级汽车，提升性能:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用专业喷漆房打造独特设计。安装车身套件、性能零件和个性化贴膜。提升速度、操控性和外观，满足客户需求，建立良好声誉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062150/extras/36ebb56f334d85bce84c39978f719293.poster.avif?t=1756490723\" width=792 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062150/extras/36ebb56f334d85bce84c39978f719293.webm?t=1756490723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062150/extras/36ebb56f334d85bce84c39978f719293.mp4?t=1756490723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经营和扩大你的汽车维修业务:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与客户谈判，制定合理价格，投资更好的设备。买卖和交换零件，最大化利润。良好的管理将吸引更多客户，带来更高收益，让你的车行蓬勃发展！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>提供专业洗车服务:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用洗车设备彻底清洁汽车。合理使用清洁用品和水，让汽车焕然一新。提升洗车技巧，升级设备，提供高品质服务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062150/extras/f9932740d084eb3dabadf9d112f8017b.poster.avif?t=1756490723\" width=800 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062150/extras/f9932740d084eb3dabadf9d112f8017b.webm?t=1756490723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062150/extras/f9932740d084eb3dabadf9d112f8017b.mp4?t=1756490723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战略管理，实现商业成功:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用高效的谈判系统，提高客户满意度。倾听客户需求，达成交易，最大化收益。做出关键决策，扩大业务，成为行业领袖。  <br>   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索充满机遇的开放世界.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前往废车场寻找稀有零件，在市场上寻找最佳交易，或在线订购高端配件。在完全互动的开放世界中建立你的汽车帝国！ <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造你的汽车维修帝国，掌握维修技能，提升客户满意度！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >改装、修理、清洗，管理你的梦想车行。<strong>立即将 Car Service Simulator 加入愿望清单！</strong></p>",
